      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REIKO BENNY (2) has missed the frame at his last couple but wasn't beaten far three back when third (16.92) at this track in a Bottom Up - Grade 5. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. IN THE CLOUDS (7) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at this track over 300m behind Dinosaur Deano (17.54) in a Grade 5. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Must be included in calculations. AUDACIOUS RACHEL (3) has a fair record and proved too strong last time to win by 1.3 lengths at this track in a handy 17.00 beating Franklin Avenue. Will go close again if runs up to latest. BE A SHADOW (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
